From c7f9642340eb61c09a05c96498fd21c9b7293770 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Maksim Ivanov <emaxx@google.com>
Date: Sun, 26 Oct 2025 18:45:31 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Support for LLVM 22 updated, as of 2025-10-25 (#439)

Update code in accordance to upstream changes. Essentially this is a partial
revert of #373.
